<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:09:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新的哥伦比亚大学管理人员文本显示，院长们讨论犹太学生的“特权”和“$$$$”，并抨击希勒尔领导人是“问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/new-columbia-administrator-texts-show-deans-talking-jewish-student-privilege-and/00000190-77d3-d2ab-a7d2-77ffef080000</link><description>虽然短信的内容之前已经报道过，但完整的交流显示，大学官员淡化了学生对反犹太主义的担忧，猛烈抨击了学校校长希勒尔，并暗示犹太学生因为金钱而受到关注</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/new-columbia-administrator-texts-show-deans-talking-jewish-student-privilege-and/00000190-77d3-d2ab-a7d2-77ffef080000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统候选人在周五决选前讨论核协议和经济制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/irans-presidential-hopefuls-talk-nuclear-deal-economic-sanctions-ahead-of-friday-runoff/00000190-7772-d705-a7f5-fffb67450000</link><description>伊朗改革派候选人表示，他将努力恢复与世界大国的核协议，而他的强硬派竞争对手则谴责他没有任何计划取消西方国家实施的经济制裁</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/irans-presidential-hopefuls-talk-nuclear-deal-economic-sanctions-ahead-of-friday-runoff/00000190-7772-d705-a7f5-fffb67450000</guid></item><item><title>定居者在约旦河西岸前哨撤离时与以色列军队发生冲突，投掷燃烧弹和石块</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/settlers-clash-with-israeli-forces-at-west-bank-outpost-throw-firebombs-stones/00000190-773a-de25-a3df-7fbbabd70000</link><description>前哨站的定居者点燃轮胎，向以色列军队投掷石块，以撤离巴勒斯坦私人土地上的建筑，该建筑已经存在了两年但没有得到执行。一名国防官员证实恐怖袭击源自前哨基地，并获得政府批准撤离</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/settlers-clash-with-israeli-forces-at-west-bank-outpost-throw-firebombs-stones/00000190-773a-de25-a3df-7fbbabd70000</guid></item><item><title>在每天接二连三的丑闻之下，内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们转移了人们对以色列不断升级的危机的注意力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-a-day-government-diverts-attention-away-from-israels-dire-situation/00000190-751c-d705-a7f5-fdff39230000</link><description>希法医院院长获释、加沙电力以及《纽约时报》的一篇报道对以色列人来说没有什么新鲜事：部长们制造并夸大丑闻，希望公众忘记他们持续的失败。政客和他们派往战场的士兵之间的鸿沟从未如此之大</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-a-day-government-diverts-attention-away-from-israels-dire-situation/00000190-751c-d705-a7f5-fdff39230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部购物中心发生刺伤袭击，两人受伤，一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-targeted-terror-cell-in-west-bank-drone-strike-palestinians-four-killed/00000190-764d-d6e9-afb6-777d76dc0000</link><description>白宫官员：拜登“可能”本月在华盛顿会见内塔尼亚胡 ■ 非法前哨撤离后，定居者向以色列军队投掷石块和燃烧弹 ■ 黎巴嫩发射火箭后，以色列国防军袭击真主党目标 ■ 白宫官员：拜登“可能”会面以色列总理访问华盛顿期间与内塔尼亚胡会面 ■ 马克龙敦促内塔尼亚胡避免黎巴嫩爆发全面战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-targeted-terror-cell-in-west-bank-drone-strike-palestinians-four-killed/00000190-764d-d6e9-afb6-777d76dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区数小时内有两人被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-people-shot-and-killed-within-hours-in-israels-arab-community/00000190-7501-d0bf-a9fd-75fbff820000</link><description>周二晚上，一名 15 岁少年也被枪杀 ■ 《国土报》的统计显示，自 2023 年初以来，以色列阿拉伯社区已发生 111 起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-people-shot-and-killed-within-hours-in-israels-arab-community/00000190-7501-d0bf-a9fd-75fbff820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部扣留了在抗议中被拘留的医生的“良好信誉证明”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/health-ministry-withholds-certificate-from-doctor-who-was-detained-at-protest/00000190-74c7-d705-a7f5-fcfff8e50000</link><description>Daphna Shochat 博士在 6 月的一次反政府集会上被拘留，后被无罪释放。即将移居英国的肖查特向卫生部申请了证明，以便她能找到工作。她被拒绝并被告知她有犯罪记录，但警方否认了这一点</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:40:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/health-ministry-withholds-certificate-from-doctor-who-was-detained-at-protest/00000190-74c7-d705-a7f5-fcfff8e50000</guid></item><item><title>一场毁灭性的言论席卷了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/an-annihilation-discourse-has-taken-over-israel/00000190-735c-d0bf-a9fd-77fe9eda0000</link><description>历史学家本尼·莫里斯和许多其他人（包括左翼人士）呼吁以色列对伊朗发动核攻击，这是毁灭一切的复仇战略的延续。我们必须趁我们还可以的时候走上街头抗议</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/an-annihilation-discourse-has-taken-over-israel/00000190-735c-d0bf-a9fd-77fe9eda0000</guid></item><item><title>26 张标志性照片讲述以色列的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/understanding-israel-through-iconic-photos-taken-before-and-after-its-establishment/00000190-73e9-d705-a7f5-fbfb976c0000</link><description>从 1948 年毁灭性的恐怖袭击到本·古里安倒立，特拉维夫博物馆展示了 27 张创造历史的标志性照片</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/understanding-israel-through-iconic-photos-taken-before-and-after-its-establishment/00000190-73e9-d705-a7f5-fbfb976c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国、俄罗斯、伊朗和以色列政府在拜登辩论失败后幸灾乐祸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/why-china-russia-iran-and-israels-government-are-gloating-after-bidens-debate-debacle/00000190-73d7-d129-afba-fff7ac9c0000</link><description>敌人欢欣鼓舞，盟友焦虑：全球对乔·拜登表现和连任机会的大量报道反映了 11 月选举的巨大利害关系 — — 从美利坚共和国的未来到世界秩序本身</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 18:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/why-china-russia-iran-and-israels-government-are-gloating-after-bidens-debate-debacle/00000190-73d7-d129-afba-fff7ac9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长声称推翻大屠杀纪念馆主席的背后有“很多原因”，但没有引用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-says-many-reasons-to-oust-yad-vashem-chair-but-doesnt-cite-them/00000190-7442-d7a4-a9dc-ff7b631d0000</link><description>一份信息自由请求显示，约夫·基什部长的办公室只收到一封投诉信，其中没有像部长所声称的那样提出不当行为或虐待行为。该投诉是由一家美国组织在 Yad Vashem 因纠纷与该组织断绝关系后发出的</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:28:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-says-many-reasons-to-oust-yad-vashem-chair-but-doesnt-cite-them/00000190-7442-d7a4-a9dc-ff7b631d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 270 天：真主党副领袖表示加沙休战是停火的唯一途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-270-hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-gaza-truce-only-path-to-cease-fire/00000190-745b-de25-a3df-7cfb14400000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列国防军高级将领寻求在加沙停火，即使这会让哈马斯暂时掌权。 ■ 10 月 7 日被杀和绑架的以色列国防军观察员的父母发誓，将继续战斗，直到针对大屠杀事件成立国家调查委员会 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府选择法官接替前首席大法官阿哈伦·巴拉克 (Aharon Barak) 在国际法院代表政府 ■ 战争结束 270 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-270-hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-gaza-truce-only-path-to-cease-fire/00000190-745b-de25-a3df-7cfb14400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列真的想被指控在加沙犯下更多战争罪吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-02/ty-article/.highlight/does-israel-actually-want-to-be-accused-of-more-war-crimes-in-gaza/00000190-73d7-dbfd-a5d1-f3d7f1ab0000</link><description>在看起来像是犯罪意图的竞争中，以色列政治人物坚持提倡折磨巴勒斯坦平民的政策，似乎是为了证明他们违反国际法的承诺</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:38:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-02/ty-article/.highlight/does-israel-actually-want-to-be-accused-of-more-war-crimes-in-gaza/00000190-73d7-dbfd-a5d1-f3d7f1ab0000</guid></item><item><title>“是时候再给和平一次机会了”：数千人聚集在特拉维夫参加以色列-巴勒斯坦和平会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-time-to-give-peace-another-chance-thousands-gather-at-peace-conference-in-tel-aviv/00000190-73b5-d705-a7f5-fbff44db0000</link><description>在一场题为“是时候了：伟大的和平会议”的活动中，在以色列人和巴勒斯坦人最黑暗的时期，竞技场上充满了对未来的希望。一位巴勒斯坦发言者说，“这个家园正在流血，如果我们现在不阻止，我们都将走上集体自杀的道路”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-time-to-give-peace-another-chance-thousands-gather-at-peace-conference-in-tel-aviv/00000190-73b5-d705-a7f5-fbff44db0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔和警方未能遏制以色列阿拉伯社区的犯罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-police-are-failing-to-stifle-crime-in-israels-arab-communities/00000190-73b4-d705-a7f5-fbfff7890000</link><description>6 月份，以色列阿拉伯社区发生了 23 起凶杀案，使年度总数达到 109 起 ■ 在国家安全部长 Itamar Ben-Gvir 的领导下，阿拉伯社区的谋杀案数量增加了一倍</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-police-are-failing-to-stifle-crime-in-israels-arab-communities/00000190-73b4-d705-a7f5-fbfff7890000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报：即使哈马斯掌权，以色列陆军领导人仍希望加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/nyt-reports-that-israeli-army-brass-want-cease-fire-in-gaza-even-with-hamas-intact/00000190-7390-d0bf-a9fd-77fa3a0a0000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列国防军官员正在推动结束加沙战争，认为这是解救人质并缓和与真主党关系的唯一机会。内塔尼亚胡反驳说，他不知道消息来源是谁，但这种情况“不会发生”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/nyt-reports-that-israeli-army-brass-want-cease-fire-in-gaza-even-with-hamas-intact/00000190-7390-d0bf-a9fd-77fa3a0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会将于7月底休会三个月，招致人质亲属批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-go-on-three-month-recess-drawing-criticism-from-hostages-relatives/00000190-7341-d0bf-a9fd-77fb7ba30000</link><description>民族联盟党提交了一项取消休会的法案，预计这将是有史以来最长的一次休会，但需要联盟的合作才能推进。亲戚们说：“只要达成协议，送回 120 名人质，你就能得到你想要的假期。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-go-on-three-month-recess-drawing-criticism-from-hostages-relatives/00000190-7341-d0bf-a9fd-77fb7ba30000</guid></item><item><title>希西家王什么时候统治？有争议的文物可能会解决圣经争议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-02/ty-article/when-did-king-hezekiah-reign-controversial-artifacts-may-resolve-biblical-controversy/00000190-7334-d084-a7dc-fbb7cbb10000</link><description>《圣经》对于犹大王在位期间反抗亚述的说法是自相矛盾的。对古物市场印章的研究声称可以打破僵局</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-02/ty-article/when-did-king-hezekiah-reign-controversial-artifacts-may-resolve-biblical-controversy/00000190-7334-d084-a7dc-fbb7cbb10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，两名以色列士兵在加沙中部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-central-gaza-combat-idf-says/00000190-72fb-d084-a7dc-faffbbad0000</link><description>30岁，军士长。来自耶路撒冷的 Nadav Elchanan Knoller（解析）和 25 岁的 Eyal Avnion 少校是周一遇难的两名士兵。另一名士兵在战斗中受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-central-gaza-combat-idf-says/00000190-72fb-d084-a7dc-faffbbad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承诺建立将生病的加沙人经埃及转移到国外接受治疗的系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-pledges-to-establish-system-to-transfer-sick-gazans-for-medical-treatment-abroad/00000190-72d1-dbfd-a5d1-f2d338b60000</link><description>以色列表示将在一周内通报该计划的最新进展。由于右翼抗议，请愿者的律师被迫在看守下离开高等法院听证会</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-pledges-to-establish-system-to-transfer-sick-gazans-for-medical-treatment-abroad/00000190-72d1-dbfd-a5d1-f2d338b60000</guid></item></channel></rss>